          target="_blank"
        >
          Check Price on Amazon &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="pros-cons">
        <div class="pros">
          <h4>What We Like</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Incredible subject tracking just like the R6 II</li>
            <li>Beautiful Canon colors straight out of camera</li>
